@startuml
' Executive-friendly architecture diagram - high level
skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 150

title Finanzas SD - Executive Architecture View

actor "PMO\nFinanzas\nSDMT" as Users
rectangle "Finanzas SD\nWeb Application" as WebApp {
  component "Projects" as Proj
  component "Rubros Catalog" as Cat
  component "Reconciliation" as Recon
  component "Reports" as Rep
}

cloud "AWS Cloud\n(Secure & Auditable)" as AWS {
  database "Project Data\n& Evidence" as Data
  component "Business Logic\n& Controls" as Logic
}

rectangle "External Systems" as Ext {
  component "SDMT\nCost Management" as SDMT
  component "SharePoint\nReports" as SP
}

Users --> WebApp : Access via browser\n(secure login)
WebApp --> Logic : API calls
Logic --> Data : Store/retrieve
Logic --> SDMT : Handoff
Logic --> SP : Reports

note right of AWS
  - Cognito authentication
  - Role-based access (PMO/FIN/SDMT/AUDIT)
  - All changes audited
  - Evidence stored securely
end note

note bottom of WebApp
  Main modules: Projects, Rubros Catalog,
  Allocation Rules, Adjustments, Cashflow,
  Scenarios, Providers, SDMT modules
end note

@enduml
